    <text type="letter">
        <body>
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <name type="place" rend="right">431 Stevens Street<ptr target="prc.00066_n1"
                        /></name>
                    <name type="place" rend="right">Camden New Jersey</name>
                    <date when="1880-02-08" rend="right">Feb. 8 '80</date>
                </dateline>
                <salute>Dear Young Man<ptr target="prc.00066_n3"/></salute>
            </opener>

            <p>I thought to-day I would send you a little picture<ptr target="prc.00066_n2"/> to show you I had not forgotten
                you or those meetings in St Louis&#8212;I have been back here about a month, &#38;
                am tolerably well&#8212;How are you getting along? Let me know if you get the
                picture all right</p>

            <closer>
                <signed rend="right">Walt Whitman</signed>
            </closer>
        </body>
